# Invoice Tracker ‚Äî Full CRUD with Blazor + EF Core (SQLite)

## 2. Solution

Build a complete invoice tracking module on top of the existing QuickBills ABP scaffold. The feature covers three aggregate boundaries ‚Äî **Customer**, **Invoice**, and **InvoiceItem** ‚Äî wired together with ABP's standard layered architecture: Domain ‚Üí Application.Contracts ‚Üí Application ‚Üí EntityFrameworkCore ‚Üí Blazor.Client.

### Key architectural decisions

| Decision | Choice | Reason |
|---|---|---|
| `Customer` base class | `AuditedAggregateRoot<Guid>` | Independent lifecycle, needs audit fields |
| `Invoice` base class | `AuditedAggregateRoot<Guid>` | Independent aggregate, owns its Items |
| `InvoiceItem` base class | `Entity<Guid>` | Owned by Invoice, never fetched standalone |
| App service base | `CrudAppService<>` for Customer; custom `QuickBillsAppService` for Invoice (needs related data) | CrudAppService covers simple CRUD; Invoice needs Include() |
| EF config | Separate `IEntityTypeConfiguration<T>` files | Keeps DbContext clean |
| Read queries | `AsNoTracking()` in list/detail queries | Performance for reads |
| Related data | Explicit `Include(i => i.Items)` in Invoice queries | ABP repos expose `IQueryable`; use `WithDetailsAsync` |
| Total calculation | Computed inside `Invoice` domain method `CalculateTotal()` | Keeps business logic out of the UI and app service |
| Permissions | Nested constants in `QuickBillsPermissions` per entity | ABP convention: `GroupName.EntityName.Action` |
| Blazor rendering | `@rendermode InteractiveAuto` pages in `QuickBills.Blazor.Client` | Consistent with the existing `Index.razor` pattern |

---

## 3. Workflow Diagram

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Blazor Page
    participant Svc as AppService
    participant Repo as IRepository
    participant DB as SQLite (EF Core)

    UI->>Svc: GetListAsync(input)
    Svc->>Repo: GetListAsync() with Include + AsNoTracking
    Repo->>DB: SELECT with JOIN
    DB-->>Repo: Entities
    Repo-->>Svc: List<Invoice>
    Svc->>Svc: Map ‚Üí InvoiceDto (ObjectMapper)
    Svc-->>UI: PagedResultDto<InvoiceDto>

    UI->>Svc: CreateAsync(CreateUpdateInvoiceDto)
    Svc->>Svc: new Invoice(GuidGenerator.Create(), ...)
    Svc->>Repo: InsertAsync(invoice)
    Repo->>DB: INSERT
    DB-->>Repo: OK
    Svc-->>UI: InvoiceDto

    UI->>Svc: AddItemAsync(invoiceId, dto)
    Svc->>Repo: GetAsync(invoiceId)   // tracked
    Svc->>Svc: invoice.AddItem(...)   // domain method recalculates total
    Svc->>Repo: UpdateAsync(invoice)
    Repo->>DB: UPDATE Invoice + INSERT InvoiceItem
    Svc-->>UI: InvoiceDto (updated total)
```

---

## 4. Files Affected

### Domain ‚Äî `src/QuickBills.Domain/`
- `Customers/Customer.cs` ‚Äî new `AuditedAggregateRoot<Guid>` entity
- `Invoices/Invoice.cs` ‚Äî new `AuditedAggregateRoot<Guid>` entity with domain methods
- `Invoices/InvoiceItem.cs` ‚Äî new `Entity<Guid>` owned by Invoice
- `Invoices/InvoiceStatus.cs` ‚Äî new enum (Draft, Sent, Paid, Cancelled)

### Application Contracts ‚Äî `src/QuickBills.Application.Contracts/`
- `Customers/Dtos/CustomerDto.cs` ‚Äî read DTO
- `Customers/Dtos/CreateUpdateCustomerDto.cs` ‚Äî create/update DTO with validation
- `Customers/ICustomerAppService.cs` ‚Äî CRUD service interface
- `Invoices/Dtos/InvoiceDto.cs` ‚Äî read DTO (includes `List<InvoiceItemDto>` + `TotalAmount`)
- `Invoices/Dtos/CreateUpdateInvoiceDto.cs` ‚Äî create/update DTO
- `Invoices/Dtos/InvoiceItemDto.cs` ‚Äî item read DTO
- `Invoices/Dtos/CreateUpdateInvoiceItemDto.cs` ‚Äî item create/update DTO
- `Invoices/Dtos/GetInvoiceListInput.cs` ‚Äî filtering/paging input (`PagedAndSortedResultRequestDto`)
- `Invoices/IInvoiceAppService.cs` ‚Äî invoice + item CRUD interface
- `Permissions/QuickBillsPermissions.cs` ‚Äî add Customer + Invoice permission constants
- `Permissions/QuickBillsPermissionDefinitionProvider.cs` ‚Äî register permissions

### Application ‚Äî `src/QuickBills.Application/`
- `Customers/CustomerAppService.cs` ‚Äî extends `CrudAppService<Customer, CustomerDto, Guid, PagedAndSortedResultRequestDto, CreateUpdateCustomerDto>`
- `Invoices/InvoiceAppService.cs` ‚Äî custom service, extends `QuickBillsAppService`, uses `IRepository<Invoice, Guid>` with `WithDetailsAsync`
- `QuickBillsApplicationAutoMapperProfile.cs` ‚Äî add mappings for all new DTOs

### Infrastructure ‚Äî `src/QuickBills.EntityFrameworkCore/`
- `EntityFrameworkCore/QuickBillsDbContext.cs` ‚Äî add `DbSet<Customer>`, `DbSet<Invoice>`, `DbSet<InvoiceItem>`
- `EntityFrameworkCore/Configurations/CustomerConfiguration.cs` ‚Äî `IEntityTypeConfiguration<Customer>`
- `EntityFrameworkCore/Configurations/InvoiceConfiguration.cs` ‚Äî `IEntityTypeConfiguration<Invoice>` (HasMany Items, cascade delete)
- `EntityFrameworkCore/Configurations/InvoiceItemConfiguration.cs` ‚Äî `IEntityTypeConfiguration<InvoiceItem>`
- `Migrations/` ‚Äî new EF Core migration (add-migration + update-database)

### Blazor UI ‚Äî `src/QuickBills.Blazor.Client/`
- `Pages/Customers/Index.razor` ‚Äî customer list + create/edit/delete modal
- `Pages/Customers/Index.razor.cs` ‚Äî code-behind
- `Pages/Invoices/Index.razor` ‚Äî invoice list with customer name + total
- `Pages/Invoices/Index.razor.cs` ‚Äî code-behind
- `Pages/Invoices/Detail.razor` ‚Äî invoice detail with inline InvoiceItems table
- `Pages/Invoices/Detail.razor.cs` ‚Äî code-behind
- `Navigation/QuickBillsMenuContributor.cs` ‚Äî add Customers & Invoices menu items
- `Navigation/QuickBillsMenus.cs` ‚Äî add menu key constants

### Localization ‚Äî `src/QuickBills.Domain.Shared/`
- `Localization/QuickBills/en.json` ‚Äî add localization keys for all new UI strings

